rows.label: tlk401006_msg0001
rows.name:
There's certainly something
not quite right going on.

rows.label: tlk401006_msg0002
rows.name:
I saw a very large wooden box being
transported on to the
Divine Beast battleship.

rows.label: tlk401006_msg0003
rows.name:
It was accounted for on the
inventory list, so most of my
colleagues think it's no problem.

rows.label: tlk401006_msg0004
rows.name:
But I honestly can't imagine what
they would want such a huge box for.
I'm worried about what might be inside.
